properties.Name: ShipmentPartyRelationshipType
properties.Description:
The nature of the relationship between the shipment and the party.

Ex:
-  Air Freight Forwarder
-  Agent
-  Authorized By
-  Beneficial Cargo Owner
-  Broker
-  Cargo Agent
-  Cartage Agent
-  Co-loader
-  Consignee (see Shipment because of importance)
-  Consignor (see Shipment because of importance)
-  Consolidator
-  Courier
 - Customs
-  Customs Clearance Service
-  Customs House Broker
-  Dealer
-  Deliver To 
-  Export Broker
-  Export Jobber
-  Freight Cashier
-  Freight Forwarder
-  Master Loader
-  Responsible Shipping Agent
-  Paid By
-  Purchasing Agent
-  Shipped By
-  Stevedore
